      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CONQUEROR (2) goes very well at this journey having never missed the frame including three wins and five placings. Recorded a 5 length win (16.83) in a Grade 6 last time at this track. Looks a key chance on best form. TERRIFIC DIXSON (4) was well fancied last time and led throughout to score (16.95) at Murray Bridge Straight in a Grade 6 over 300m. Capable of going well again. JUST A NUISANCE (8) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 1.5 lengths at Angle Park in a handy 19.82 beating Royale Maple. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from four starts. Can go close again if runs up to latest figure. COMPTON CHINOOK (1) can run a bold race on best form.",
